WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.931 --> 00:00:13.651
 Free motion quilt, echo quilt, presser for cut work No. 44C 

00:00:14.554 --> 00:00:25.894
 Attach the 44C presser and let the sewing machine recognize it (depending on the model). 

00:00:29.972 --> 00:00:34.352
 Lower the feed dog. 

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:41.300
 Select straight stitching, zero swing width, set the needle base in the center, and set the needle position at the end of sewing to the bottom. 

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:45.580
 When sewing thick cloth, reduce the presser pressure. 

00:00:46.255 --> 00:00:52.155
 Place the quilt core between the upper and lower fabrics. If necessary, strike the needle or do sewing. 

00:00:52.460 --> 00:01:00.100
 Remove the presser and quilt three layers of fabric. It does not matter whether you trace on the draft line or completely free. 

00:01:01.095 --> 00:01:08.035
 Be sure to move the dough evenly. Then the seams will be even. 

00:01:08.740 --> 00:01:15.320
 A thin cross attached to the presser foot indicates the position of the needle and serves as a guide. 

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:24.400
 At the place where the sewing is finished as the final process, do the 3-4 needle stop sewing and do automatic thread trimming. 

00:01:35.706 --> 00:01:39.986
 Cut work 

00:01:40.904 --> 00:01:47.381
 Attach the embroidery machine to the sewing machine. Lower the feed dog and attach a needle plate for cut work. 

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:57.280
 Recognize the embroidery machine on the sewing machine and select the cutwork design. 

00:02:00.710 --> 00:02:07.450
 Set the fabric on the embroidery frame, or place the fabric on the embroidery frame on which you set the adhesive stabilizer. 

00:02:08.313 --> 00:02:18.873
 Remove the upper thread and the needle. Then set the cut work tool and set the knife position to 1. 

00:02:26.554 --> 00:02:32.234
 Check the design and attach the embroidery frame to check the position. 

00:02:40.621 --> 00:02:47.521
 Start the sewing machine with the hand start button. 

00:02:49.420 --> 00:02:56.220
 When the knife position 1 part is finished, advance to 2-4 in order. 

00:02:58.540 --> 00:03:04.260
 After cutting in all positions, pick up the cut ones. 

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:07.160
 Replace the cutting edge. 

00:03:09.658 --> 00:03:14.838
 Loosen the screw with the attached thin hexagonal rod and remove the cutting edge. 

00:03:16.340 --> 00:03:23.280
 Insert the blade and tighten the screw. 

